Guest editors have included some rather… *influential* figures. Director [J. J. Abrams](/J._J._Abrams), filmmaker [James Cameron](/James_Cameron), architect [Rem Koolhaas](/Rem_Koolhaas), former US President [Barack Obama](/Barack_Obama), director [Christopher Nolan](/Christopher_Nolan), tennis player [Serena Williams](/Serena_Williams), and video game designer [Will Wright](/Will_Wright_(game_designer)). A mixed bag. Some visionaries, some politicians, some entertainers. What do they all have in common? They’re names people recognize. And *Wired* knows names.

